===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{uncountable}} A hard brittle material that is produced through burning of nonmetallic [[mineral]]s at high temperatures
#: ''Joan made the dish of '''ceramic'''.''
# {{countable}} An object made of this material
#: ''Joe had dozens of '''ceramics''' in his apartment.''

